{"tid":997323,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"張家界散客拼團劏客! 張家界遊記分享","createTime":"2019-01-27T05:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T05:32:48.000Z","uid":233370,"like":7,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"50b35c4c1d6498550a5b5acea274e72fd6fb284a","tid":997323,"uid":233370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"張家界散客拼團劏客! 張家界遊記分享<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8VCLH0XnxAM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8VCLH0XnxAM&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1ad8e8d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8VCLH0XnxAM</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然我知道大家都好聰明唔會中伏, 但既然我柒左就分享下啦, 同埋巴打開左個新channel, 將會有其他內容的影片, 啱睇就支持下啦!<br />\n<br />\n故事內容<br />\n<br />\n我們在港已計劃好所有行程和住宿，原意是全程自由行，而不是參加散客拼團。及後因在張家界汽車中心附近遇到騷擾，坐上的士打算離開現場。但因原先訂下的民宿就在汽車中心附近，為避免再次被騷擾，經司機介紹下輾轉來到「酒店」/旅行社 (詳見youtube影片資料) 。由於當時已是晚上十時，我們舟車勞頓了一整天，只想趕快找個地方安置。接待人員一番遊說，並勸我們退了原來的民宿，見價錢和行程大致符合預算，加上他們拿出先前已有港人報團的案例，不虞有詐決定參加 ，並退了原來的民宿。<br />\n<br />\n套路之深難以想像，合約列明團費包括景點門票、導遊費、交通、住宿和飲食；但不包景點內的索道等運輸，亦沒有清楚列明每日行程。詢問時接待人員回避問題(因為他們一早已知道第二天會發生什麼事)，故意讓人誤解為不是行程必須。直至翌日上車後才突然提出所有人都必須額外收費$520/680才能上山(實際只會一上一下索道$76，百龍天梯$72)，沉沒成本論讓一眾團友乖乖交錢，有團友說這是張家界的潛規則。三日兩夜行程團費加上額外收費約人民幣二千多元，折合港幣$2500元左右，對很多人而言不算高昂，但有同行的國內團友一家十四口跟團，完全就是被旅行社和導遊宰割，亦讓我們大失預算，作為遊客觀感極差。<br />\n<br />\n後來回想再整理思緒後，才頓悟騷擾我們的人、的士司機和旅行社櫃台人員跟本就是同一伙，相信他們一早已寫好劇情，故意造成並讓遊客相信張家界市中心治安不好，從而說服你去住他們的酒店並參加他們的散客團。而經旅行社負責人一句整個張家界旅遊市場都是這樣的解釋後，我們更相信這是集團式誤導遊客。<br />\n<br />\n大量網民遇到同樣的事情:<br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/639421.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F639421.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c0b16910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/639421.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/651747.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F651747.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8f6fb6b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/651747.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/568506.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F568506.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=848fab0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/568506.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/633071.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F633071.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=e8eb6ef4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/633071.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/528021.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F528021.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5f5cf5a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/528021.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/631266.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F631266.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=c4ef0280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/631266.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/681796.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F681796.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=6eaabf54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/681796.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://ts.voc.com.cn/question/view/707377.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fts.voc.com.cn%2Fquestion%2Fview%2F707377.html&d=%2BFEzSYEz1bTH5AdSBpjkdKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=1f27f3ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_bla